==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Dredge up a needle from the great ocean.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà hăi lāo zhēn

===Idiom===
'''[[大]][[海]][[撈]][[針]]'''

# [[needle in a haystack]].

===Alternate forms===
